response.original_title: Starrcast V: Insight With Special Guest Claudio Castagnoli
response.overview: On July 30th Insight with Chris Van Vliet is live on FITE as part of Starrcast V events. The event features a special guest - it's the pro wrestling star Claudio Castagnoli.  Tune in and find out what Claudio Castagnoli has to say after 4 months of absence, about his decision to leave WWE and sign with AEW. All that and much, much more!  Order Starrcast V with The Roast of Ric Flair today and watch Insight with Chris Van Vliet, featuring special guest Claudio Castagnoli right here on FITE!
response.title: Starrcast V: Insight With Special Guest Claudio Castagnoli
